ina Elias","date":"July 29, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts the month of Ramadan, performs the prayers, and makes the Hajj pilgrimage to the House, it is a duty upon Allah to forgive him whether he emigrates in the path of Allah or\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27515,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/11\/ramadan-jibreel-quran-twice\/","url_meta":{"origin":18883,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Gabriel comes to review the Quran twice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Fatimah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel would come to me to revise the Quran once every year. This year he revised with me twice. I do not think it means anything but that my term will come to an end. Verily, you will be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":457,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/27\/essentials-pillars-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":18883,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Essentials of salvation are pillars of Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A bedouin\u00a0came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, sho